The paper deals with representation problems for graphs, specifically unit interval graphs and unit circular-arc graphs. These are topics that fall under computational geometry (cs.CG) and graph theory (cs.DS, cs.GT). The paper also involves algorithms and complexity analysis, which are relevant to computer science theory (cs.CC) and discrete mathematics (cs.DM).
